    "description": "Compact and high-performance fire alarm control panel for monitoring small facilities, supporting up to 8 conventional sensor groups (max 240 devices). Features a large LCD display for easy operation and programming, with integrated sensor group display. Includes four programmable relays, two sounder outputs (EN 54-13), and interfaces for fire/fault transmission units and fire brigade panels. Designed for high flexibility and reliable false alarm suppression, with event memory and alarm counter. Comes with German front foil. Central control unit, complete with system software including installation material, installation, commissioning and operating manuals, operating book for BMA, but without batteries.",
